https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34d879a762218b6279b0c322608157e6f9c00273","tid":1538490,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"bea485e7cea97e133bbea0eec39ecc9be103cea0","tid":1538490,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"係喎<br />\n<br />\n01出POST 官方認證分化報嚟"},{"pid":"7a65f04af7965de221171bdf6bc50a2a895fefc2","tid":1538490,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAsR52D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAsR52D.png&h=de91a106&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3860a82013f7600bf5ffcb72f32ec458b3a9b36","tid":1538490,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?